\section{Theory}{

The modal series solution for a sphere expands backscatter from a spherical
scatterer in spherical Bessel/Hankel modes. The form function is:

\eqn{
 f_{bs} = -\frac{i}{k_w} \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} (-1)^n (2n+1) A_n,
}
}

